                                         skos:altLabel "Z-score normalization"@en ,
                                                       "standardization"@en ;
                                         skos:definition "Standard normalization, or standardization, is a data preprocessing technique that transforms features to have a mean of 0 and a standard deviation of 1, resulting in a distribution with unit variance."@en .


###  https://rsna.org/roadmap/ROADMAP_00128
