                                         skos:definition "The Moving Picture Experts Group (MPEG) standards support compression, decompression, processing, and coded representation of moving pictures, audio, 3G graphics, and haptics."@en .


###  https://rsna.org/roadmap/ROADMAP_00132
<https://rsna.org/roadmap/ROADMAP_00132> rdf:type owl:Class ;
                                         rdfs:subClassOf <https://rsna.org/roadmap/ROADMAP_00119> ;
                                         dc:source <https://doi.org/10.48550/arXiv.2410.13174> ;
                                         rdfs:label "concordancia multimodal mejorada"@es ,
                                                    "enhanced multi-modal concordance"@en ,
                                                    "增强的多模态一致性"@zh ;
                                         skos:altLabel "MMC+"@en ,
                                                       "enhanced multi-modal concordance index"@en ;
                                         skos:definition "MMC+, an enhanced framework for scalable drift monitoring, builds upon the CheXstray framework that introduced real-time drift detection for medical imaging AI models using multi-modal data concordance."@en .


###  https://rsna.org/roadmap/ROADMAP_00133
