###  https://rsna.org/roadmap/ROADMAP_00169
<https://rsna.org/roadmap/ROADMAP_00169> rdf:type owl:Class ;
                                         rdfs:subClassOf <https://rsna.org/roadmap/ROADMAP_00248> ;
