###  https://rsna.org/roadmap/ROADMAP_00174
<https://rsna.org/roadmap/ROADMAP_00174> rdf:type owl:Class ;
                                         rdfs:subClassOf <https://rsna.org/roadmap/ROADMAP_00660> ;
                                         rdfs:label "guideline"@en ;
                                         skos:altLabel "AI checklist"@en ,
                                                       "AI guideline"@en ,
