                                         rdfs:subClassOf <https://rsna.org/roadmap/ROADMAP_00126> ;
                                         rdfs:comment "Feature extraction can reduce computational cost and improve machine learning model performance. It reduces noise and redundancy by distilling complex data (e.g., images, text, sensor data) into key characteristics. It often follows initial preprocessing like cleaning and normalization."@en ;
