###  https://rsna.org/roadmap/ROADMAP_03416
<https://rsna.org/roadmap/ROADMAP_03416> rdf:type owl:Class ;
                                         rdfs:subClassOf <https://rsna.org/roadmap/ROADMAP_03381> ,
                                                         [ rdf:type owl:Restriction ;
