                                                       "pixel-level label"@en ;
                                         skos:definition "Annotation applied to one or more pixels of an image, either as a segmentation or as a simple geometric shape such a rectangle (bounding box)."@en .


###  https://rsna.org/roadmap/ROADMAP_03480
<https://rsna.org/roadmap/ROADMAP_03480> rdf:type owl:Class ;
                                         rdfs:subClassOf <https://rsna.org/roadmap/ROADMAP_03479> ;
