###  https://rsna.org/roadmap/ROADMAP_03482
<https://rsna.org/roadmap/ROADMAP_03482> rdf:type owl:Class ;
                                         rdfs:subClassOf <https://rsna.org/roadmap/ROADMAP_03355> ,
                                                         [ rdf:type owl:Restriction ;
                                                           owl:onProperty <https://rsna.org/roadmap/ROADMAP_00198> ;
                                                           owl:hasValue <https://rsna.org/roadmap/ROADMAP_00234>
                                                         ] ,
