###  https://rsna.org/roadmap/ROADMAP_03483
<https://rsna.org/roadmap/ROADMAP_03483> rdf:type owl:Class ;
                                         rdfs:subClassOf <https://rsna.org/roadmap/ROADMAP_03479> ;
                                         rdfs:label "anotación de segmentación"@es ,
                                                    "segmentation annotation"@en ,
                                                    "分割标注"@zh ;
                                         skos:altLabel "segmentation label"@en ;
                                         skos:definition "Segmentation annotation involves labeling specific pixels in an image into a specific category or class. Unlike bounding boxes, which simply outline an object, segmentation annotation provides precise boundaries."@en .


###  https://rsna.org/roadmap/ROADMAP_03484
<https://rsna.org/roadmap/ROADMAP_03484> rdf:type owl:Class ;
