###  https://rsna.org/roadmap/ROADMAP_03500
<https://rsna.org/roadmap/ROADMAP_03500> rdf:type owl:Class ;
                                         rdfs:subClassOf <https://rsna.org/roadmap/ROADMAP_03484> ;
