###  https://rsna.org/roadmap/ROADMAP_00332
<https://rsna.org/roadmap/ROADMAP_00332> rdf:type owl:NamedIndividual ,
                                                  <https://rsna.org/roadmap/ROADMAP_00329> ;
                                         <https://rsna.org/roadmap/ROADMAP_00198> <https://rsna.org/roadmap/ROADMAP_00171> ,
