                                         rdfs:label "CONSORT-AI item 01a"@en ;
                                         skos:definition "Identification as a randomized trial in the title. Indicate that the intervention involves artificial intelligence/machine learning in the title and/or abstract and specify the type of model. State the intended use of the AI intervention within the trial in the title and/or abstract."@en .


###  https://rsna.org/roadmap/ROADMAP_00333
