###  https://rsna.org/roadmap/ROADMAP_00611
<https://rsna.org/roadmap/ROADMAP_00611> rdf:type owl:NamedIndividual ,
                                                  <https://rsna.org/roadmap/ROADMAP_00492> ;
                                         <https://rsna.org/roadmap/ROADMAP_00198> <https://rsna.org/roadmap/ROADMAP_00173> ,
                                                                                  <https://rsna.org/roadmap/ROADMAP_00255> ,
                                                                                  <https://rsna.org/roadmap/ROADMAP_00256> ;
                                         <https://rsna.org/roadmap/ROADMAP_04089> <https://rsna.org/roadmap/ROADMAP_00485> ;
                                         rdfs:comment """Tier 1: complete sharing of the code
Tier 2: allow a third party to evaluate the code for accuracy/fairness; share the results of this evaluation
Tier 3: release of a virtual machine (binary) for running the code on new data without sharing its details
Tier 4: no sharing"""@en ;
                                         rdfs:label "MI-CLAIM item 19"@en ;
                                         skos:definition "Reproducibility: choose appropriate tier of transparency."@en .


